IMAPAccount gmail-cobus
Host imap.gmail.com
User cobus.jjimjilbang@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.oh-no-insecure-password"
PassCmd "emacsclient -e \"(my/lookup-password :host \\\"gmail.com\\\" :user \\\"cobus.jjimjilbang@gmail.com\\\")\" | cut -d '\"' -f2"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-cobus-remote
Account gmail-cobus

MaildirStore gmail-cobus-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/email/gmail-cobus/
Inbox ~/email/gmail-cobus/Inbox

Channel gmail-cobus
Far :gmail-cobus-remote:
Near :gmail-cobus-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Expunge Both
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount fatcow-john
Host imap.fatcow.com
User john@wassilak.com
PassCmd "emacsclient -e \"(my/lookup-password :host \\\"fatcow.com\\\" :user \\\"john@wassilak.com\\\")\" | cut -d '\"' -f2"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore fatcow-john-remote
Account fatcow-john

MaildirStore fatcow-john-local
Path ~/email/fatcow-john/
Inbox ~/email/fatcow-john/INBOX/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel fatcow-john
Far :fatcow-john-remote:
Near :fatcow-john-local:
Patterns *
Expunge Both
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *